Message.message: ...delicious hope...I must taste it! Come to me...
...oh, did you...hope...to escape? Don't try to deny it. I can smell the belief on you like a pungent cheese...
...how very cunning you've been, finding your way here...
AE: No further questions, please. Go now! My cats' lives depend on you. Go!
LDV: What calculations? How could you know that?
AE: You see all these vacuum tubes? Orange openings lead back towards this room. Purple ones lead...elsewhere. My calculations reveal that one leads...to THE EXIT, because reasons.
LDV: Do you know how to escape? Please! I must return to my inventions!
AE: No further questions, please! Now, onto the burning issue. How to get out of here? My poor cats will be desperate to be fed, after all...
AE: Hello! My name is ALBERT EINSTEIN and unless my eyes decieve me, you are LEONARDO DA VINCI. Your very being here proves my theory of General Relativity!
[Transmission] ...i'm a nursery of sorts, for the brightest of clients...
[Transmission] ...and a funeral pyre for ancient giants...
Yep, just as unpleasant as last time.
I really need to get out of here.
